headline: Motorola Solutions’ New AI Assist Suites Targets Public Safety Workflows And Growth
summary: Motorola Solutions (NYSE:MSI) has launched Assist Suites, a portfolio of AI-driven tools for public safety agencies. The new offering is designed to support emergency response, dispatch, and field reporting by turning agency data into actionable intelligence. Assist Suites focuses on role-based solutions intended to reduce data overload, support staffing constraints, and improve decision making for frontline teams. headline: What Motorola Solutions (MSI)'s New Assist Suites AI Platform Means For Shareholders
summary: Earlier this week, Motorola Solutions launched Assist Suites, a portfolio of role-based AI tools that unify 911 audio, video, and radio data to support faster emergency response, officer safety, and more accurate, auditable police reporting. A distinctive aspect of Assist Suites is its Narrative Assist feature, which cross-checks officers’ accounts against multiple verified data sources while preserving clear human oversight and an audit trail of all AI suggestions.
